<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7915400>
    dc:description "Figs 104–108.Stylogaster irwini sp. n.: (104) habitus, lateral view (♂ holotype); (105) antenna,lateral view (♂ holotype); (106) frons (♂ holotype); (107) abdomen, dorsal view (♂ holotype); (108) wing (♂ paratype, locus typicus). Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7915400/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7915402>
    dc:description "Figs 109–114. Terminalia (♂) of Stylogaster irwini sp. n. (paratype from locus typicus): (109) surstylus, lateral view; (110) same, ventral view; (111) cercus, lateral view; (112) teeth at ventral conjunction of cerci, dorsal view; (113) phallus sheath of hypandrium, lateral view; (114) sperm pump and ejaculatory apodeme.Abbreviations: ce – cercus; su – surstylus. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7915402/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

